{"tid":1674346,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子在連儂牆撕毀紙張並襲擊他人　判100小時社服令","createTime":"2019-10-25T07:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T07:45:07.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bddf87f36928ef0b81c57e69d97ace8bd9af53aa","tid":1674346,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:08:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">一名貨車司機在屯門一道連儂牆撕毀文宣紙張，被途人用手機拍攝，貨車司機襲擊對方並推到牆上，令對方後腦受傷</span>。司機早前承認一項襲擊致構成身體傷害罪，在屯門裁判法院被判100小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n54歲被告司徒文輝沒有律師代表，在庭上表示一時衝動才犯案。裁判官判刑時表示，法庭不能接受暴力行為，理解被告對社會運動有意見，可能不開心，但他需要照顧家庭，沒本錢衝動，又告誡他如果再次行經連儂牆使用暴力，後果自負。<br />\n<br />\n案發在今年8月4日晚上，途人在屯門新和里行人天橋連儂牆，目擊被告撕海報並拍攝約8秒鐘，被告不滿而襲擊對方。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488192-20191025.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488192-20191025.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTRnwB9%2FpnwrfV4lJUXhph6I%3D&h=3e6d1d27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488192-20191025.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7d547d08\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488192-20191025.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"0cd861e8b0cc15dffa67dd16186f86635c43084c","tid":1674346,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a1c896808bb7fb3b5b0d7c0a487c7ebcd23e8a","tid":1674346,"uid":54181,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:09:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50be746af63bb6cd15d54f3e7a1288a1e6e379d5","tid":1674346,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:11:37.000Z","msg":"藍屍輕判<br />\n<br />\n黃絲重判<br />\n<br />\n這就是香港法